          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teasers & Trailers",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Aperçu de l'histoire : Les Traces",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/07/70239714/c7b69d309843f53dae154e2066b59a08_846121441948502661.jpg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "20/09/2020",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube :",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(128, 192, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "HoYoverse :",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "https://genshin.hoyoverse.com/fr/news/detail/103718",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Bande-annonce de la version 2.6 « Zéphyr sur le jardin violet »",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/06/237301566/6d179f9c1e87c9add5dd8dc9a5ad0ffe_1740772523316611927.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "18/03/2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Le vent traverse la nature et rencontre la poésie du jardin violet.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "La lumière de la vallée éclaire un coin d'obscurité.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Sur le reflet de l'eau, tel un miroir, se dévoilent les histoires du passé...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube :",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Bande-annonce de la version 3.5 « Souffle des alizées »",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/06/237301566/9b6ccdb41e742840308daac5efb843c3_6308549419918263562.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "17/02/2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Certains disent que le destin se cache dans le vent, comme le parfum des fleurs, la pluie et la rosée...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Pour eux, telle est l'insurmontable loi de la nature.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "D'autres aspirent à trouver leur destin et vont jusqu'à tenter de le tracer eux-mêmes.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Mais tout cela n'est-il pas justement pas le fruit du sort ?",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube :",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Bande-annonce de la version 4.7 « Un éternel rêve entrelacé »",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/06/237301566/9b42d35f9a503427ac6a0d50d08badc2_6712732388128120438.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "24/05/2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Les gens se sentent souvent prisonniers de leur passé.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Tous ces regrets non résolus,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "et toutes ces questions sans réponse...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Tout cela pourrait rentrer dans l'ordre à l'avenir,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "ou peut-être que cela continuera à se répéter en rêve.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube :",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Court-métrage « La voie non empruntée »",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/14/170542231/6761bae9b3f1a9984dc80837e9c4f0db_7695006065886866566.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "24/05/2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "... Mais",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "au moins, tu es toujours là, quelque part dans le monde.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "La trace de la comète qui a jadis traversé le ciel,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "est désormais la voie non empruntée par laquelle je te cherche.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube :",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Émoticônes",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
